data.description: Come see this beautiful 2 story home located in the heart of Norfolk! This home boasts 4 beds 2.5 bath, and over 2100 SQFT of open concept living space! Custom paver patio installed 2017, deck refurbished and new railing installed in 2020, stainless steel appliance package installed 2016. Located just minutes from the naval base and shopping at the outlets! You don't want to miss out on this one. Solar panels will be paid off with acceptable full price offer!
